'''Imuhaɣ''' d agdud [[Imaziɣen|amaziɣ]] yettidiren deg [[Aneẓruf|Uneẓruf]] n [[Tafriqt]]. Akal-nsen d Aneẓruf (Idurar n [[Tasili]], n [[Ayer]] di [[Niger]], atg.). 

Yernu imi ay zgan tddun ɣef udar, ttreggizen (teddun) nutni d lmal-nsen (iɣersiwen n-sen d ileɣman) seg wemkan ɣer wayeḍ, wwḍen ɣer waṭas n tmiwa di Tefriqt. Imuhaɣ xulḍen aṭas n yegduden ifriqiyen ay ten-id-iqerben neɣ yellan ɣer tama n-sen, nitni fkan-asen daɣ-nni wwin-d aṭas seg-sen. Ass-a, nezmer ad naf Imuhaɣ di Nijer d [[Mali]], am akken nezmer ad naf kra n trebbaɛ-nsen neɣ n waggayen di [[Čadd]], [[Burkina Faso]] akk d [[Nijerya]]. 

Deg wenḍul n Uneẓruf (Niger akk d Mali), aṭas n yegduden ifriqiyen ay yettidiren ɣer tama n Yimuhaɣ, nezmer ad d-nebder seg-sen [[Ibambaraten]], [[Ifulanen]] akk d [[Isarakuliyen|Yisarakuliyen]]. Kra seg yegduden-agi kessen lmal am Yimuhaɣ, di lweqt i deg wiyaḍ xeddmen tafellaḥt neɣ akal. Tuɣ (yella), wakal n wenẓul n Uneẓruf kkan (uɣent) deg-s isaffen, d aya ay t-yerran d agilal, amakken (meḥsub) yelha (igarrez) i tfellaḥt. 

==Aẓar n w-awal==

Awal ''Amuhaɣ'' deg asuf, ''Imuhaɣ'' deg asget naɣ daɣen ''Kel Tamacaq'' ad yaf aẓar-is deg awal ''Amaziɣ'', ''[[Imaziɣen]]'' deg asget. D aɣdebbu n imuhaɣ ig ǧǧan ad yeḍru cwit n usnifel ger w awalen agi, maca di tilawt d yiwen. <br/>
Isem n tutlayt ''Tamacaq'' yekkad seg ''[[Tamaziɣt]]''.

